{"data":{"title":"金字塔原理","description":"","date":"2026-05-21T00:04:21.000Z","updated":"2026-05-21T08:04:21.081Z","language":"zh-CN","comments":false,"url":"reading/499B1AA5082E8EA93865FEC078B36113/index.html","cover":null,"images":[],"content":"<html><head></head><body><blockquote>\n<p>共 4 条摘录，最近更新：2023-07-12</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2023-07-12</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">金字塔结构的巨大价值就在于它迫使你在理清思路时，<br>从视 觉上使纵向的疑问/回答式对话关系清晰化</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《金字塔原理》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2023-07-12</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">表述必须具有明确的归纳或演绎关系，<br>但不可同时既具有归纳关系，<br>又具有&nbsp;演绎关系</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《金字塔原理》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2023-07-12</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">演绎性思想组合是由几个承前启后的论述组成的。<br>第一个思想是对当今 世界上的某种现象的表述；<br>第二个思想是对该句子的主语或谓语所作的表述;<br>第三个思想则说明了以上两种表述同时在世界上存在时所具有的隐含意义</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《金字塔原理》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2023-07-12</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">读者只有 在需要了解问题的答案时才会去找答案；<br>如果读者没有这种需要，<br>就不会提&nbsp;出任何疑问；<br>反之亦然</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《金字塔原理》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  let flipSwitchTimer = null\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', event => {\n    if (event.target.closest('a')) return\n    const card = event.target.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail .zhaizhai-flip-card')\n    if (!card) return\n    if (flipSwitchTimer) {\n      clearTimeout(flipSwitchTimer)\n      flipSwitchTimer = null\n    }\n    const container = card.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail')\n    const cards = container ? container.querySelectorAll('.zhaizhai-flip-card.is-flipped') : []\n    const isFlipped = card.classList.contains('is-flipped')\n\n    cards.forEach(item => {\n      if (item !== card) item.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    })\n\n    if (isFlipped) {\n      card.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    } else {\n      const hasOtherFlipped = [...cards].some(item => item !== card)\n      if (hasOtherFlipped) {\n        // Close previous card first, then open target card for smoother switch.\n        flipSwitchTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n          card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n          flipSwitchTimer = null\n        }, 120)\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n      }\n    }\n  })\n})()\n</script>\n</body></html>","raw":"---\ntitle: 金字塔原理\ndate: 2026-05-21 08:04:21\ntype: page\naside: true\ncomments: false\n---\n\n> 共 4 条摘录，最近更新：2023-07-12\n\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2023-07-12</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">金字塔结构的巨大价值就在于它迫使你在理清思路时，<br>从视 觉上